OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry with plenty of sunshine,
OL,6,Falthough it will often be hazy.
OL,7,FBecoming very warm or perhaps hot for
OL,8,Fmost places away from the coast, where
OL,9,Fcooling onshore breezes will occur.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FDry with a mix of cloudier
OL,12,Fspells and clear periods. Winds will
OL,13,Fbecome very light and variable,
OL,14,Fleading to a chance of patchy mist
OL,15,Fdeveloping.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
